      public Nfa toNfa() throws InvalidRegexException, StateExistsException
      Transforms RegEx to NFA. Complexity: O(n * m * Concat) - n is number of characters of expression, m number of operands, and it is multiplied with complexity of function
      Returns:
      NFA representation of RegEx
      Throws:
      InvalidRegexException - if there is invalid character in regex
